headline: Game On: Discord reportedly in talks for IPO in 2025
summary: “Game On” is The Fly’s weekly recap of the stories powering up or beating down video game stocks. headline: Can Best Buy (BBY) Survive Trump’s Tariff Onslaught?
summary: Last week’s implosion of big-box retailer Best Buy (BBY) was predictable based on prevailing economic and political winds. Although the company reported solid figures in its most recent fourth-quarter earnings report, the overwhelming concern centered on the Trump administration’s tariffs and the prospect of an ugly trade war.
